  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >HELP NINA!</h2><br>After the great devastation, Nina abandons her system and tries to reach the promised land she heard about, in deep space. It's your mission to help her!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXCITING LOW-RESOLUTION SHOOTER</h2><br>This exciting shooter will take you back to the 8bit/16bit era. Written in C++ for supreme performance, retro gaming fanatics are going to have a blast trying to achieve the highest score.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Steam achievements<br></li><li>Steam leaderboard<br></li><li>Vicious bosses<br></li><li>A diverse selection of weapons<br></li><li>A specific scoring system</li></ul>",
